rd and stream from multiple cameras,\n- work in impressive and exciting locations and have engaging and productive meetings,\n- make the space your own: brand and save your meeting space and reuse it at anytime,\n- connect  to your team and plan activities: play basketball, chess, chat next to the fireplace or even visit an art exhibition\u2026\n\nBuild greater things and have a better communication in Beyondreal virtual offices, which do not just give you a place to work, but immerse you in a engaging workflow.", "short_description": "Beyondreal is an enterprise collaboration suite that allow you to:\n- whiteboard with ease, use your corporate tools or Beyondreal self made applications, \n- create a space that you can save and reuse with multiple screens, 3D tools, stickers and much more,\n- use your full photorealistic body avatar, and face recognition to give presentations, create smart maps, show products, or play basketball and just relax and chat with a friend at the campfire."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://beyondreal.life/privacy-policy-2/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://beyondreal.life/terms-and-conditions/", "publisher_name": "Anasaea", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://beyondreal.life/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1063584910766706"}, {"id": "2687655338230691"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": ["EDUCATIONAL", "PRODUCTIVITY", "SOCIAL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_mod